Welcome To CSC Workspaces

Our upscale, collaborative work environment is located at West mall  The Queensway with easy access to the QEW. Our distinctive combination of state-of-the-art functionality, elegant design, and concierge level service are a few reasons why  CSC Workspaces is re-imagining the workplace.

you require the flexibility of our co-working desks, the consistency and structure of a fully furnished private office, or access to our professionally appointed boardrooms and event spaces that will elevate your next meeting or business gathering

 we have designed flexible workplace solutions paired with innovative and elevated services to create an inspiring, community-based space that will help you to make the most out of each business day
